quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  17,99,"Enee, Й“ee yi'aali, wonnde Alla On TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin ko O HattanЙ—o nde O tagata yeru maЙ“Й“e, O waЙ—ani Й“e lajal [caate] sikke alaa e maggal. TooГұooЙ“e Й“en salii si wanaa yeddugol"
  17,100,"Maaku: \"Sinndo onon hiЙ—on marunoo ngaluuji Hinnayee Joomi an on, ontuma, on jogitotono kulol nafkugol, neЙ—Й—anke on wonii nguddo"
  17,101,"GomЙ—ii Men okkiino Muusaa Aayeeje jeenay Й“annguЙ—e, lanndii Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila Й“en tuma nde o arunoo Й“e Fir'awna wi'ani mo: \"Min dey miЙ—o sikkumaa ko an yo Muusaa ko a mbilЙ—aaЙ—o"
  17,102,"Maaku: \"GoЙ—ii hiЙ—a anndi jippinaali Й—ee si wanaa JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin Aayeeje [yi'eteeЙ—i]. Min dey miЙ—o sikkumaa ko an yo Fir'awna ko a halkiiЙ—o"
  17,103,O faalaa nde o dillinta Й“e ka leydi Men yooli mo e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e makko Й“e denndaangal
  17,104,"Men Daalani Й“aawo makko Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila Й“en: \"HoЙ—ee ka leydi, si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, Men adday on ko on muuЙ“iiЙ“e=fiiliibe"
  17,105,"Ko sabu Goonga Men telliniri nde, ko sabu Goonga nde tellii, Men nuliraali ma si wanaa [ko a] wewlinoowo=beltinoowo e jertinoowo"
  17,106,"E Qur'aanaare Men Й“anngini nde fii yo a janngannde yimЙ“e Й“en e dow deeЖҙere, Men jippini nde jipinnde"
  17,107,"Maaku: \"GomЙ—inee nde, maaЙ—un wata on gomЙ—in, pellet, Й“en okkaaЙ“e ganndal ko adii nde si [nde] janngaama e taweende maЙ“Й“e Й“e suuyiray wokkuЙ—e ko Й“e sujjooЙ“e"
  17,108,"ЖҒe wi'a:Senaade woodanii Joomi amen,nde wonnoo Fodoore Joomi amen nden ko waЙ—oore"
  17,109,"HiЙ“e suuyira wokkuЙ—e Й“e wulla [Alqur'aana on] Й“ayda Й“e yankinaare"
  17,110,"Maaku: \"Noddiree Mo Alla maa noddiro Mo Hinnorante, kala no noddirЙ—on Mo, ko Kanko InЙ—e MoЖҙЖҙe Й—en heeranii, wata a fenГұin julde maaЙ—a nden wata a suudu nde Й—aЙ“Й“u hakkunde Й—un laawol"
  17,111,"Maaku: Yettoore nden woodanii Alla On Mo jogitaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o laatanaaki Mo kafidaaЙ—o e Laamu laatanaaki Mo tedduЙ—o mo O huykinantoo, Mawnin Mo Mawninndee"
  18,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On TippinЙ—o e dow JeyaaЙ—o Makko on Deftere nden O waЙ—anaali nde ooГұaare"
  18,2,"Feewunde fii yo o [NulaaЙ—o on] hulЙ“inir lepte sattuЙ—e immorde ka Makko o weltinira gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, Й“en Й“e no golla MoЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й—in wonnde no woodani Й“e Njoddi MoЖҙЖҙiri"
  18,3,"Ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“ooЙ“e e nder makko [Neema on] poomaa"
  18,4,"O rentina Й“en wi\"uЙ“e: \"Alla jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o"
  18,5,"Ganndal alanaaЙ“e e mun, wanaa baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e woodani, mawnii konngol wonungol e yaltude e kunnduЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wowlaali si wanaa fenaande"
  18,6,"Bala jo'o an a tanpinay hoore-maa e dow batteeji maЙ“Й“e, si gomЙ—inaali ndee Yewtere ka suno"
  18,7,"Menen Men waЙ—ii ko woni kon ka hoore leydi cuЙ—aari mayri, fii yo Men jarribo Й“e ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“urata moЖҙЖҙinnde golle"
  18,8,Menen ko Men waЙ—ooЙ“e ko woni kon e hoore mayri boowol yoorungal
  18,9,"Kaa a sikku no yimЙ“e fammeere=wimmba nden e binndi Й—in, Й—un wonu immorde e Aayeeje Amen hawniiЙ—e"
  18,10,"Tuma nde sukaaЙ“e Й“en sorunoo ka fammeere, Й“e wi'i: \"Joomi amen okku men immorde ka MaaЙ—a Hinnayee=yurmeende newinaNaa men kadi e fiyaake amen peewal"
  18,11,Men piyi e dow noppi maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka nder fammeere limoore duuЙ“i
  18,12,"Refti Men immintini Й“e fii yo Men fenГұinir gonndal ko honnde e mojobe=pelle Й—en Й—iЙ—i Й“uri moftude [limoore] ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“i kon dummunne"
  18,13,"Menen MeЙ—en fillanaade ma kumpital fii maЙ“Й“e e Goonga, Й“en Й—on, ko sukaaЙ“e gomЙ—inЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e Men Й“eydani Й“e Peewal"
  18,14,"Men haЙ“Й“i e dow Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e tuma nde Й“e darinoo, Й“e wi'i: \"Joomi amen ko JeyЙ—o On kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, men noddataa ko woori Mo reweteeЙ—o, gomЙ—ii haray men wi'ii ontuma [konngol] fantungol"
  18,15,"ЖҒee yimЙ“e amen, Й“e jogitike ko woori Mo reweteeЙ—i, ko haaanunoo ko yo Й“e addu e dow maЙ“Й“e dalil Й“annguЙ—o. Ko hommbo Й“uri tooГұude ko foti e on fefindiiЙ—o fenaande o fawi e Alla"
  18,16,"Tuma nde woЙ—Й—itinoЙ—on Й“e e ko Й“e rewata kon ko woori Alla, Й“e soroyi ka fammeere Joomi mon fontani on e Yurmeende Makko nden O newinani on e fiyaake mon neweende"